While testing BSERVDEV-12819 I found that the source build instructions (https://developer.atlassian.com/bitbucket/server/docs/latest/how-tos/building-bitbucket-server-from-source-code.html) have a few issues:

* The docs refer to SQL Server 4.0.2206 driver version but the build expects 4.2.6420
* The docs say to run {{mvn3.sh}} but the source distro contains {{mvn339.sh}}
* The built artifact doesn't actually appear to work with the {{mvn cargo:run}} command as per the docs
* Trying to run through IDEA gives an error about the {{docs.version}} property - even adding the extra step from our [internal instructions|https://extranet.atlassian.com/display/BSERV/HOWTO+-+Running+Bitbucket+Server+in+IDEA] doesn't seem to help?
* This instruction doesn't work as well {{mvn cargo:run}}

